value.0: Clad in pure white robes, the Grandmaster of the Frozen Hand is neither tall nor muscled, but his unblinking icy stare promises a painful death to any who show him a mote of disrespect. He clutches a solid iron staff mottled by a thin layer of rime in his gnarled claws, seemingly ready to shatter those who succumb to his gelid powers.

A shock of short black hair and a swarthy complexion immediately set this athletic, lithe figure apart from the others in the hall. Pale blue eyes that steam with a white mist leap out in stark contrast to his body's earthy tones. Like the rest of the Frozen Hand this ascetic is garbed in sheer white, though his cloth is a smart tunic and leggings rather than a more traditional robe.

The training room is dominated by an ice rink that has seen a number of hard slips and falls. The condition of the ice seems to vary in sections, from smooth, flat ice to uneven and jagged, making for a more fickle, treacherous environment upon which to try and maintain balance while facing other combatants.

[OOC: You can also attack this object to "shadow box" and to try out the different styles in the ACP!]
